 <p>
 Landscaping, lawn care, and outdoor service crews are in the sun six days a week. The gear has to work harder than a standard uniform. We outfit Vegas landscaping companies with wide-brim sun protection hats (not baseball caps — actual sun hats with neck coverage), moisture-wicking performance tees and tanks for the mowing crews, and embroidered polos for sales reps, account managers, and the crew lead who shows up to estimate.
 </p>
 <p>
 Branded gear for landscaping isn't just about the crew — it's a rolling billboard. Every truck that drives through a neighborhood with branded team gear and a matching logo on the trailer wrap is a lead generator. We handle branded work gloves, logo water bottles and coolers for the crew (Vegas heat is a real safety issue and hydration gear with your logo is both useful and visible), embroidered quarter-zips for the office, and promo items for client gifting after a big install.
 </p>
 <p>
 Common orders: wide-brim sun hats, performance tees and tanks, embroidered sales polos, branded work gloves, logo water bottles and coolers, embroidered quarter-zips, and client gifting sets.
 </p>
